344
00:21:03.863 --> 00:21:06.366
Just like old friends.

345
00:21:08.200 --> 00:21:09.336
Tell me.

346
00:21:09.436 --> 00:21:11.871
Is this part of a formal investigation

347
00:21:11.971 --> 00:21:13.773
