What if his RSF friends found out.

386
00:23:17.263 --> 00:23:21.000
Osman had requested
political asylum in the U.K.?

387
00:23:21.834 --> 00:23:24.270
They'll think he used
this whole London mission

388
00:23:24.370 --> 00:23:26.773
