403
00:24:47.186 --> 00:24:48.454
Not at all. Dr. Zahir.

404
00:24:48.521 --> 00:24:50.089
Actually. more of a solution.

405
00:24:54.661 --> 00:24:56.428
Come on.

406
00:25:19.118 --> 00:25:20.753
