407
00:25:21.554 --> 00:25:24.223
Relax. You're safe.

408
00:25:24.323 --> 00:25:27.259
I need your phone and your electronics.

409
00:25:30.529 --> 00:25:32.031
My laptop is in my case.

410
00:25:32.131 --> 00:25:33.633
